title: Lf team/create one
body:
Hey guys, S4 jungler main, supp secondary LF team, (or make one)

looking for a team who has the intention to stay together, win or lose, improve and learn to synergies.
My champion pool is essentially anything, off the top of my head j4, lee, yi, sej, pan, trundle, vi, naut, xin, rek', mal, ww, udyr are the ones i've been playing more lately.

Hit me up, IGN Tazo

replies.body: Jump on http://RetreatHellGaming.com we have plenty of New Zealand and Aussie players wanting to make ranked teams.
